Package com.bobocode.bring.web.servlet.http

Enum Class HttpStatus

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<HttpStatus>
com.bobocode.bring.web.servlet.http.HttpStatus
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<HttpStatus>, Constable
public enum HttpStatus extends Enum<HttpStatus>
Enumeration representing HTTP status codes as defined in the HTTP/1.1 specification. Each constant in this enum represents a specific HTTP status code, along with its series and reason phrase.

For more information about HTTP status codes, refer to the HTTP/1.1 specification: RFC 7231 - Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP/1.1)

Since:
1.0
Author:
Blyzhnytsia Team
